    "description": "<p><strong>Sunny</strong> is the presence of harsh, overbearing sunlight, making fires burn hotter, and photosynthesis seemingly improving. Generally, Fire- and Grass- Types benefit from Sunny Weather.</p><p><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Effects:</span></strong></p><ul><li>Fire-Type Attacks deal 30% more damage, and Water-Type Attacks deal 30% less damage.</li><li>Grass-Type creatures gain 30% to their Movement Allowances, and their SPD is increased 15%.</li><li>Fire-Type Attacks are resisted one step less by Water-Types.</li><li>Creatures cannot be Frozen, and Frozen creatures are cured of Frozen.</li><li>Fire-Type Moves and Physical-Category Steel-Type attacks have a 10% chance to inflict Burn 5. Attacks that would already cause Burn instead increase their chance to Burn by 10%.</li></ul>"
  },
